headline: UBS Affirms Neutral Rating on Baxter International (BAX)
summary: Baxter International Inc. (NYSE:BAX) is one of the 12 best healthcare stocks to buy now. On June 11, UBS reiterated a ‘Neutral’ rating on the stock and a $35 price target. The Neutral stance follows a meeting with the company’s Head of Investor Relations. According to UBS, the company has demonstrated momentum across its portfolio […]
